Yemeni Prisoner Killed, 15 Wounded in Clash With Security Forces

-- B y   M o h a m m e d   H a t e m
-- 
2011-03-08T13:43:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-08/yemeni-prisoner-killed-15-wounded-in-clash-with-security-forces.html
Yemeni police clashed with inmates
inside the capital’s Central Prison, killing one and injuring
more than 15, according to Abdulrehman Barman, executive
director of Sajeen, a non-governmental human rights
organization.  The prisoners were shouting slogans demanding a change in
the regime, he said by telephone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mohammed Hatem in Sana’a at 
 mhatem1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net  